<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>Pielgal Gamnuom !</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Pielgal gam nuom leh ka Lalpa,
 Hehpih hung lang ding chu;
 Thil zel ingka thepna huihpi;
 Leh gitloh thim nuoiah.

[V2]
 Dan takleh thepna meipi leh,
 Thimna a beih tieng leh;
 Lang zel ina, A hehpihna,
 Nawpna tuikhuk lul chu.

[V3]
 2. Khawvel buoina haw pawt sanin,
 Hehpihna Lal deihum;
 Pak ka ngaklah, nawpna chullo,
 Van zaila hawih chu san.

[V4]
 3. Khawvel buoina laka Lalpa.
 Na hehpih min lopi;
 Pakcha seng puo'ng ka, Hukdampa,
 Ka gitlohna'n ei nang.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>201</hymn_number>
</song>